{"tid":2452731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[廣東話 ? ] 三藩市華裔老婦無故受襲拾棍還擊　白人男子被打至躺擔架送院","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T11:43:48.000Z","uid":57677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6375fb79ee5e2f7bbe3210c3b3a294f993823f71","tid":2452731,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/asian-woman-attacked-san-francisco-fights-back/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fasian-woman-attacked-san-francisco-fights-back%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=1c1d79ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbsnews.com/news/asian-woman-attacked-san-francisco-fights-back/</a><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DennisKPIX/status/1372241168663076864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1372241168663076864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsan-francisco-man-attacks-elderly-asian-woman-she-fights-back-2021-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDennisKPIX%2Fstatus%2F1372241168663076864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1372241168663076864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.insider.com%252Fsan-francisco-man-attacks-elderly-asian-woman-she-fights-back-2021-3&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=ad67e418\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDennisKPIX%2Fstatus%2F1372241168663076864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1372241168663076864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.insider.com%252Fsan-francisco-man-attacks-elderly-asian-woman-she-fights-back-2021-3&h=6d89a99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DennisKPIX/status/1372241168663076864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1372241168663076864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsan-francisco-man-attacks-elderly-asian-woman-she-fights-back-2021-3</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"0f25bc7d540265537149a83b0ec8d5b6e5e158df","tid":2452731,"uid":57677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"兩岸, 國際 發佈時間 19.03.2021 06:23最後更新時間 19.03.2021 08:41 美國三藩市灣區再發生以亞裔為目標的襲擊事件，1名75歲華裔老婦星期三朝早在街上等過馬路時，被1名39歲白人男子揮拳打傷眼部，事主隨即拾起木棍還擊，兩人事後送院治理。 當地一間電視台的體育總監目擊事發過程，由他拍下事發之後的片段可見，遇襲的婆婆眼部受傷，需要拿著冰袋敷臉，另一隻手則仍拿著木棍，並向警察用廣東話表示「佢蝦我呀、佢蝦我呀」。懷疑施襲的男子就嘴角流血，需要躺在擔架床送院。 遇襲的婆婆接受電視台訪問時說，遇襲時感到震驚，當時的反應是立即還擊，自己受到很大創傷和非常害怕。她的女兒就表示，媽媽左眼紅腫流血，仍然睜不開，亦不能進食，遇襲之後感到非常害怕，不敢出門。 警方拘捕白人男子，並指他案發前不久，亦在同一地區襲擊一名83歲亞裔男子，正調查是否涉及種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2383634&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a1546146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383634</a>"},{"pid":"eed21271f3e1c514ebbfbd63d725342434eb9303","tid":2452731,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"中共又攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6c01100b950b2c59addc6e47216e08c305c057","tid":2452731,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"台山話"},{"pid":"8559c65d25f266b7dd1a5538a5d7047ac13c41c7","tid":2452731,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f6c01100b950b2c59addc6e47216e08c305c057","tid":2452731,"uid":311285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"台山話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"可能一九四九年以前已經移民咗去<br />\n<br />\n暫時未fact check到佢黃定藍<br />\n<br />\n遲早日本人都波及"},{"pid":"89043138ab07efecb8c1e088d9405c648e3a80b7","tid":2452731,"uid":28765,"like":15,"dislik